column5: I was offered a new area to hunt deer,turkeys and fowl.  The deer area will be posted later,Once I have my set ups done,but the fowl area is well,WOW.Can only amagine what it will be like when the corn comes down.I need to find me a canoe.  I used my field/fishing camera,not my good one.

that looks like a good spot they were sure firing the guns on sunday morning, bottom end of cooks bay  foggy has hell I don't know what they could see to shoot  there goes my frog fishing the slop, didn't want my butt shot off
Did you bring the fishing rod Brian?  lol!!!!
Looks like someone is going to be eating duck this winter
That's a lot of decoys you have out there Brian.
To funny Dan.     I dont eat the heads Paul.  I do slice the breasts to make sure there isnt any.
NICE!!!!!  I have a canoe we could drag out there!!!
I have a canoe and all the gear. Just say the word and we can go  S.
I'm sensing an OFC waterfowl G2G in the near future Brian
